WEBVTT

00:08:59.346 --> 00:09:01.695
We all hate.

00:09:02.568 --> 00:09:06.818
And I do not mean that
in some abstract, generic sense.

00:09:06.842 --> 00:09:09.043
I mean all of us ...

00:09:10.571 --> 00:09:12.111
me and you.

00:09:13.684 --> 00:09:18.929
That sanctimonious pedestal of superiority
on which we all place ourselves,

00:09:18.953 --> 00:09:22.280
that they are hateful and we are not,

00:09:22.304 --> 00:09:26.178
is a manifestation
of the essential root of hate:

00:09:26.202 --> 00:09:29.731
that we are fundamentally good
and they are not,